Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.96,0:00:21.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs38\pos(450,390)\1c&HFFFFFF&}海底两万里 / {\fs18}蓝宝石之谜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.97,0:00:30.03,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讨厌懦弱的人 无法背叛蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.11,0:00:36.27,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在做梦之前 我想翱翔天际
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.21,0:00:44.14,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,心中的音乐盒开启 发出声响
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.22,0:00:51.39,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一点一滴演奏出幸福与勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.46,0:01:00.17,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在在你眼前 有着无限的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.24,0:01:05.64,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,言语是永远的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.71,0:01:10.61,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't forget to try in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.68,0:01:15.45,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爱比宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.39,0:01:22.22,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,更能照亮一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.86,0:01:28.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,距今约一百年前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.77,0:01:33.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强、娜蒂亚、玛莉与大王 逃出沉入深海的鹦鹉螺号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.97,0:01:36.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,漂流至某座无人岛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.91,0:01:40.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跟在万能潜水艇上 要什么有什么的生活完全相反
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.98,0:01:45.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强他们现在得靠自己的力量 想办法生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.78,0:01:48.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然而娜蒂亚却不晓得 大自然的恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.05,0:01:51.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟对无人岛上的生活 产生了期望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.45,0:01:55.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,甚至还说出想要一辈子 都留在这座岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.39,0:01:58.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚究竟在想些什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.00,0:02:02.36,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,#24 林肯岛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.76,0:02:32.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.10,0:02:40.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你搞什么啊 娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.47,0:02:42.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉还想睡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.14,0:02:44.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们还要睡到什么时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.84,0:02:47.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再睡下去 小心眼珠子融化掉喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.08,0:02:49.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是我们到昨天为止…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.41,0:02:52.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,经历了那么多事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.38,0:02:55.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,从今天起 我们要在这座岛上生活
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.79,0:02:59.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不改变之前的生活步调可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.36,0:03:03.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,首先要为这座南方乐园命名
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.86,0:03:05.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我昨天想了一整晚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.33,0:03:07.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.03,0:03:09.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,林肯岛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.80,0:03:11.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,林肯岛？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:15.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是解放黑奴的 美国总统的名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.24,0:03:15.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.01,0:03:18.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还有这个峡湾就叫船长湾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.24,0:03:19.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,船长湾？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.64,0:03:22.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为船长室在这里靠岸是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.21,0:03:23.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.15,0:03:25.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再来那边的沙滩 则叫作『娜玛大海滩』
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.95,0:03:27.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜玛大海滩？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.65,0:03:30.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是取自娜蒂亚 玛莉与大王的名字是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.92,0:03:32.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.52,0:03:37.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么我的名字不在里头？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.23,0:03:39.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,『娜玛大海滩』这个名字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.93,0:03:42.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,里头就只有娜蒂亚 玛莉与大王的名字不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.67,0:03:45.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么独缺我的名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.94,0:03:46.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.00,0:03:48.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜强玛大海滩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.54,0:03:51.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好饶舌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.98,0:03:55.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说久了一定就会习惯的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.24,0:03:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对吧 大王
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.61,0:04:02.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我总觉得有件事比命名更重要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.52,0:04:07.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要是你不喜欢我取的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.52,0:04:09.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就别用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.23,0:04:11.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你到底是怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.23,0:04:13.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,变得跟之前的你完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.30,0:04:17.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 思考了一整晚之后 我重生了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.67,0:04:19.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不会再愁眉不展
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.04,0:04:21.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也不会再乱发脾气
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.34,0:04:25.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我靠自己打破自己的壳 已经成长了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.61,0:04:28.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我已经不是 从前的那个娜蒂亚了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.34,0:04:32.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对 我已经重生为 南方岛屿的娜蒂亚了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.38,0:04:37.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我已经从蛹羽化成蝴蝶了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.02,0:04:40.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,早安 水薙鸟纳基特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:43.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,早安 野兔萨奇诺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.39,0:04:48.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,早安 森林的动物们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.83,0:04:50.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜…娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.20,0:04:53.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你只是为了这件事 而把我们拉来这里的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:04:54.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.97,0:04:57.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们得从船长室把东西搬出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.34,0:04:59.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为救援到来之前做准备
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.58,0:05:01.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有一堆事得做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.91,0:05:06.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我决定要跟科学和文明 断绝一切关系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.55,0:05:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以没有做那些事的必要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.82,0:05:13.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今后我要和森林自然共存
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.12,0:05:14.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再见了 强
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.70,0:05:23.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了？ 没有人要跟我走吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.13,0:05:25.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一个人也能活得好好的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.04,0:05:30.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她愈来愈奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.57,0:07:37.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.83,0:07:39.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.80,0:07:42.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是我发明的海水过滤装置
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.34,0:07:44.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海水不是很咸不能喝吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.68,0:07:47.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以要先将海水煮沸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.31,0:07:52.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样就能将盐分留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.38,0:07:56.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,经过沸腾 水变成水蒸气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.55,0:07:58.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,静置一段时间 就会恢复成水
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.15,0:07:59.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然后聚集在那个盆子里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.79,0:08:01.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这么一来就有淡水喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.59,0:08:03.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么样？很棒的发明吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.33,0:08:07.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然后呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.48,0:08:25.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 强
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.08,0:08:28.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快点快点 快点来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.62,0:08:29.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.85,0:08:32.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 可以看到船喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.00,0:08:41.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.94,0:08:53.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.01,0:08:57.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你并不相信 自然和动物的力量对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.68,0:09:01.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你就一辈子 留在这座无人岛上后悔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.42,0:09:04.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,后悔自己相信科学的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.32,0:09:05.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哪有这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.12,0:09:08.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,奇怪？玛莉跟大王呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.43,0:09:12.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再见了 强
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.00,0:09:16.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们要快乐地在大自然中生活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.17,0:09:18.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别走 也带我一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.37,0:09:21.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.74,0:09:23.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:26.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等等我 等等我 娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.04,0:09:28.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别走 娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.01,0:09:31.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别扔下我一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.52,0:09:38.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.42,0:09:40.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原来是梦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.59,0:09:43.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 是船喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.86,0:09:45.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我就是为了这种时候而做的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.70,0:09:47.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.75,0:10:10.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我明明是为了 这种时候而做的说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.60,0:10:23.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了？大王
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.44,0:10:28.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚\N娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.88,0:10:43.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,(马铃薯)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.32,0:10:45.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.96,0:10:48.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爱逞强又讲不通
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.45,0:11:11.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.12,0:11:18.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.83,0:11:27.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.03,0:11:33.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好方便喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.20,0:11:35.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这么方便的东西 究竟是谁发明的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.04,0:11:37.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真让人惊讶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.64,0:11:40.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没想到你居然 连开罐器都不晓得
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.74,0:11:42.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这在鹦鹉螺号可是常识喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.91,0:11:46.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为强都不帮忙做事 才会不晓得
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.88,0:11:48.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对吧 大王
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.45,0:11:54.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,总之 这样就不用 再麻烦大王开罐头了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.23,0:12:00.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我要开动了\N开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.54,0:12:11.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.34,0:12:12.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,底
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.37,0:12:13.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.44,0:12:14.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.38,0:12:15.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.41,0:12:16.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.35,0:12:18.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,打开啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.28,0:12:23.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.65,0:12:27.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是东方的叉子 叫作『筷子』
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.53,0:12:35.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,习惯了也满好用的 手也会变得灵活不少
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.87,0:12:38.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那也得先习惯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.00,0:12:42.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有了方便的工具 生活也会跟着丰富起来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.94,0:12:46.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算没有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.31,0:12:47.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那些工具
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.71,0:12:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我还是有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.78,0:12:50.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在马戏团里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.08,0:12:51.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,锻炼的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.28,0:12:52.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,毅力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.78,0:12:54.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.49,0:13:03.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.43,0:13:11.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚好慢喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.94,0:13:13.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.47,0:13:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,饭明明都准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.24,0:13:19.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她只要回来就好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.78,0:13:21.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.28,0:13:26.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你好像在等老婆回来的丈夫喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.88,0:13:30.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,总…总之从今天起 我们得开始找粮食了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.95,0:13:34.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,从船长室拿出来的粮食 已经吃完了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.39,0:13:36.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉捡到的罐头呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.66,0:13:39.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那些罐头太旧了不能吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.29,0:13:42.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,盖子会膨起来 就表示里头已经腐烂了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.10,0:13:44.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人家好失望喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.64,0:13:54.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天的午餐是鱼吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.34,0:13:56.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,钓得到的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.71,0:13:58.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉想吃肉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.62,0:14:04.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是森林里有可怕的神明在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:10.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等着看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.99,0:14:13.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我才不会认输呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.43,0:14:45.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都没钓到半条鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.20,0:14:49.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,钓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.97,0:14:51.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你好厉害喔 大王
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.50,0:14:52.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.84,0:14:59.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.51,0:15:01.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刚才那条鱼很大耶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:05.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很大…外海… (『大』音近『外海』)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.51,0:15:07.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对了 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.18,0:15:09.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不到外海去是钓不到大鱼的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.04,0:15:35.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强好好喔 有带玩具来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.98,0:15:38.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉也好想要玩具喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.55,0:15:41.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉 这并不是玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.18,0:15:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这叫百科全书
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.65,0:15:46.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,里头记载了从哲学到宇宙 有关这个世界上的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.56,0:15:50.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还有人名辞典 与世界地图的附录
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.09,0:15:52.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 帮玛莉做玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.73,0:15:53.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,晚一点喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.40,0:15:55.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人家觉得好无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.87,0:15:59.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.30,0:16:01.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们来玩文字接龙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.81,0:16:05.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就从玛莉开始喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.14,0:16:07.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,『玛莉』所以是…i
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.58,0:16:11.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,i…喵(a)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.25,0:16:12.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,a？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.31,0:16:15.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就…冰淇淋(mu)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.92,0:16:17.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,mu喵(a)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.82,0:16:18.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,a？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.75,0:16:19.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,杏仁(do)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.79,0:16:20.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,do喵(a)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.49,0:16:23.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,熨斗的结尾是n不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.33,0:16:24.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,红豆(zu)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.26,0:16:24.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,zu喵(a)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.03,0:16:26.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,芦笋(su)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.30,0:16:27.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,su喵(a)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.43,0:16:28.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,苹果派(i)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.63,0:16:29.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,i喵(a)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.26,0:16:30.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鲍鱼(bi)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.83,0:16:31.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,bi喵(a)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.83,0:16:32.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蚂蚁(ri)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.70,0:16:33.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,ri喵(a)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:34.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鸭子(ru)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.30,0:16:34.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,ru喵(a)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.90,0:16:36.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,亚马逊(n)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.98,0:16:41.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王你好狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.41,0:16:45.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全部都用『喵』结尾 哪有这种接龙嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.58,0:16:46.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.05,0:16:49.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强陪我接龙 好不好？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.72,0:16:50.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,晚一点喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.92,0:16:53.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跟玛莉玩接龙啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.96,0:16:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,晚一点 晚一点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.06,0:17:01.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,上勾了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.70,0:17:07.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是大鱼喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.94,0:17:16.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.22,0:17:24.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,钓到了\N钓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.32,0:17:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是船\N是船
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.06,0:17:35.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第三次必能成功
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.60,0:17:43.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂 我们在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.64,0:17:50.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还是算了 玛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.55,0:17:51.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.22,0:17:55.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚不会走的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.13,0:18:13.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刚才好可惜喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.04,0:18:16.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,漏网之鱼总是最大条的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.05,0:18:26.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,又在破坏大自然了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.88,0:18:29.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,船？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.27,0:18:47.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大丰收
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.27,0:18:52.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我好不容易才晒干的说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.34,0:18:57.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,救命…来人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.61,0:18:59.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.62,0:19:01.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.05,0:19:04.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚跟船长室 一起被冲到外海了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.06,0:19:09.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.12,0:19:11.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样我会被愈冲愈远的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.33,0:19:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拜托 森林的动物们 来救救娜蒂亚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.70,0:19:21.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拜托 鱼儿们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.38,0:19:27.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.71,0:19:29.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么谁都不来救我？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.52,0:19:37.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.55,0:19:39.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.22,0:19:42.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.63,0:19:53.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刚才真是好险 娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.67,0:19:57.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,难怪无论我怎么呼唤 鱼儿们就是不肯过来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.34,0:20:01.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原来是你们把鱼全都抓走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.68,0:20:02.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.34,0:20:03.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是那也没有办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.88,0:20:08.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要是不那么做 我们就会饿死耶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.85,0:20:09.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.19,0:20:12.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鱼儿们一定能够谅解的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.74,0:20:37.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你怎么会跑去船长室？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.45,0:20:40.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.35,0:20:43.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你帮我把那张立体照片 一起拿出来了是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.65,0:20:47.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为那是你的宝物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.59,0:20:49.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.89,0:20:54.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对不起 我老是说些任性的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.50,0:20:57.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我真是个爱逞强又讲不听的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.70,0:21:01.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只依赖自然是活不下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.74,0:21:05.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,既然生为人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.84,0:21:07.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要以人的身分生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.98,0:21:11.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就必须用自己的双手发明创造
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.22,0:21:15.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,距今两亿年前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.35,0:21:19.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个地球还是爬虫类的全盛时代
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.52,0:21:21.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它们之所以会灭亡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.36,0:21:26.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是因为它们将环境改变为 适合它们生存的环境
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.16,0:21:28.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因此繁殖过多
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.46,0:21:31.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就跟目前的人类一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.87,0:21:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以我们必须创造出 能让自然与人类共存的科学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.11,0:21:41.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爬虫类的血是冰冷的 但人类的血却是温热的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.98,0:21:43.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想相信的并非科学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.98,0:21:46.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而是创造出科学的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.98,0:21:47.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.45,0:21:49.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.72,0:21:50.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.69,0:21:52.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个…你来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.16,0:21:56.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是玛莉画的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.93,0:21:58.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不知道是什么时候画上去的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.96,0:22:02.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的名字叫玛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.10,0:22:07.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,于1885年4月10日 在法国马赛出生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.50,0:22:11.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是我完全不记得马赛的事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.94,0:22:17.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为我才出生没多久 就搬到佛得群岛的马哈尔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.08,0:22:21.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爸爸跟妈妈在那里死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.08,0:22:25.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是玛莉不是孤单一人 所以一点都不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.46,0:22:29.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚是玛莉的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.79,0:22:30.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,动不动就生气
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.03,0:22:32.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且非常挑食
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.83,0:22:35.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她说她会和动物说话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.46,0:22:37.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 我从来都没看过
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.83,0:22:41.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是玛莉还是最喜欢娜蒂亚了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.27,0:22:43.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强是娜蒂亚的老公
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.57,0:22:45.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,老是跟娜蒂亚夫妻吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.04,0:22:49.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是我只要一说 他们在夫妻吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.11,0:22:50.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,两个人就会一起生气
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.78,0:22:52.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很过份吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.71,0:22:54.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强总是在做奇怪的玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.75,0:22:56.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要他陪我玩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.15,0:22:59.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他却老是回答说『晚一点』 都不肯陪我玩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.69,0:23:02.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是他不像娜蒂亚那样 爱发脾气
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.36,0:23:04.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以我也最喜欢强了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.03,0:23:07.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉的老公 大王
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.13,0:23:09.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其实它原本是娜蒂亚的男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.97,0:23:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,却被玛莉抢来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.30,0:23:16.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是大王也说它比较喜欢玛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.27,0:23:19.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们是两情相悦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.37,0:23:20.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然有点老成
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.01,0:23:23.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也最喜欢大王了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.28,0:23:25.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她在写什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.95,0:23:28.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,非常挑食 动不动就生气？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.65,0:23:30.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一点也没错
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.35,0:23:32.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.65,0:23:34.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你看 又生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.66,0:23:37.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样才不算生气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.66,0:23:40.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,或许我是稍微淘气 活泼了点
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.93,0:23:43.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,个性也稍微急躁了些
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.23,0:23:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有时会比较多愁善感
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.43,0:23:48.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但我以前在马戏团的时候 可是既可爱又受欢迎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.74,0:23:50.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还真不害臊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.77,0:23:53.70,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,待续
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.71,0:24:02.59,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,该怎么应付心中的焦急才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.65,0:24:07.68,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就要看不清远方的梦想了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.76,0:24:12.06,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我喃喃自语 仰望星空
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.13,0:24:21.00,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,与你的约定耀眼闪烁着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.07,0:24:31.00,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Try 安慰的话语 是传达不到内心的风
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.08,0:24:39.96,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然背负的不安逐渐膨胀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.03,0:24:44.19,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但这是我自己的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.26,0:24:48.82,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一个人应该也不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.90,0:24:57.83,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使跌倒或感到迷惘 仍然有明天
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.09,0:25:09.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚生病了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.72,0:25:12.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她好像是因为吃了奇怪的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.79,0:25:15.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原来娜蒂亚是个贪吃鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.83,0:25:19.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强出去找能治病的药草…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.87,0:25:24.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海底两万里 下一回 『第一次的吻』
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.84,0:25:26.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有点难为情
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.04,0:25:28.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 还是请大家要看喔
